ail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc2.staticflickr.com%2F2%2F1758%2F42059087004_68d999eebc_b.jpg&h=d8418e5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而一護班同學仔個個都靚仔靚女!<br />\n朽木同戀次就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8951ec7cf0ef11398bda77e6c287321ff281a2","tid":819040,"uid":187368,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T18:06:08.000Z","msg":"作為fans好滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成套嘢風格同原作幾似<br />\n特別啲角色嘅日常互動(會你推我撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n又會出下一護同露琪雅個名同身份<br />\n配樂功勞都好大，幾rock<br />\n節奏掌握得唔錯<br />\n<br />\n日本仔CG越嚟越好<br />\n啲打鬥又做得幾爽<br />\n而且調色好有電影感，色水到位<br />\n<br />\n一護同露琪雅嘅演員做得幾好<br />\n佢地嘅互動好有CP感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (雖然漫畫明明唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n露琪雅個造型係唔似原作，但啲戲做得幾好，特別喊戲個段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋演員好cute</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n一護個frd同漫畫一樣夠囇on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n茶渡就好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n織姫就一般 <span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個胸唔似</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最大敗筆係戀次同白哉<br />\n成個cosplay佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd2d0d8cb1cd81598ca670196ff154815ef569a","tid":819040,"uid":187368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T18:11:52.000Z","msg":"不過劇情都係有少少為做而做<br />\n呢點係漫畫改編嘅通病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a57af2a03540c8a290b02d0aed3672cf288244f","tid":819040,"uid":3695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"